      Speedup: 1.87x
      - Added autotune to the mask-free interior kernel, cleanup kernel, and small-shape fallback kernel. The sweep varies spatial tile shapes, cleanup block size, num_warps, and num_stages, while keeping `grf_mode` as a launch compiler option (`"auto"`) rather than placing it in `triton.Config`, to avoid runtime `TypeError` on Intel XPU. The main-region alignment was changed so every autotuned `BPH/BPW` candidate covers a valid mask-free interior region with a grid lambda dependent on autotune meta-par

